methods.compact:
**Incompatible overloads text - text from the first overload:**

Compact the values in values by retaining only the positions where retainValues is true.

*Overload 1*  
  :param values: (io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.WritableBooleanChunk<? extendsio.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.Attributes.Any>) - the input and output chunk of values
  :param retainValues: (io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.BooleanChunk<io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.Attributes.Any>) - a chunk parallel to values, a value is retained in the output iff retainedValues is true
  
*Overload 2*  
  :param values: (io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.WritableChunk<? extendsio.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.Attributes.Any>) - a chunk of values, input and output
  :param retainValues: (io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.BooleanChunk<io.deephaven.db.v2.sources.chunk.Attributes.Any>) - the values to retain
